# MDX Content Standards

## Blog Post Structure

- Folder: `content/blog/YYYY-MM-DD--slug/index.mdx`
- `assistant` script: `npm run assistant` creates posts with this format

## Frontmatter (required)

```yaml
---
title: "Post Title"
slug: "kebab-case-slug"
description: "SEO description"
date: YYYY-MM-DD
lastUpdated: YYYY-MM-DD
tags:
  - TagName
  - AnotherTag
---
```

- `slug`: kebab-case, no leading/trailing slashes, no spaces or dots
- `tags`: use values from `FRONTMATTER_TAGS` in `@constants` (General, Coding, MDX, etc.)

## Optional Frontmatter

- `image`: optional og:image path
- `searchIndex`: boolean, default true (pagefind indexing)

## MDX Directives

- Asides: `:::note`, `:::tip`, `:::caution`, `:::danger` (with optional title: `:::note Custom Title`)
- Playground: `@lekoarts/remark-sandpack` with `Playground` component
